Integrated Role of Nutrition and Physical Activity for Lifelong Health.

Koehler K(1)(2), Drenowatz C(3).

Author information:
(1)Department of Sport and Health Sciences, Technical University of Munich, 
80992 München, Germany. karsten.koehler@tum.de.
(2)Department of Nutrition and Health Sciences, University of Nebraska-Lincoln, 
Lincoln, NE 68583, USA. karsten.koehler@tum.de.
(3)Division of Physical Education, University of Education Upper Austria, 4020 
Linz, Austria.

It is well established that healthy nutrition and physical activity (PA) are key 
lifestyle factors that modulate lifelong health through their ability to improve 
