Nutritional Factors, DNA Methylation, and Risk of Type 2 Diabetes and Obesity: 
Perspectives and Challenges.

Parrillo L(1)(2), Spinelli R(3)(4), Nicolò A(5)(6), Longo M(7)(8), Mirra 
