Patterns of Life Lost to Cancers with High Risk of Death in China.

Yan Y(1), Chen Y(2), Jia H(3), Liu J(4), Ding Y(5)(6), Wang H(7), Hu Y(8), Ma 
J(9), Zhang X(10), Li S(11)(12).

