Mortality, morbidity, and risk factors in China and its provinces, 1990-2017: a 
systematic analysis for the Global Burden of Disease Study 2017.

Zhou M(1), Wang H(2), Zeng X(1), Yin P(1), Zhu J(3), Chen W(4), Li X(3), Wang 
L(1), Wang L(1), Liu Y(1), Liu J(1), Zhang M(1), Qi J(1), Yu S(5), Afshin A(2), 
