Erratum in
    Lancet. 2020 Jul 4;396(10243):26.

Comment in
    Lancet. 2019 Sep 28;394(10204):1115-1116.
    Lancet. 2019 Oct 26;394(10208):1516.
    Lancet. 2019 Oct 26;394(10208):1515.
    Lancet. 2019 Oct 26;394(10208):1515-1516.
    Lancet. 2019 Oct 26;394(10208):1515.
